      <title>大选后美国房屋建筑商信心达到七个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/us-homebuilder-sentiment-reaches-seven-month-high-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于销售预期上升且市场对特朗普政府将减轻监管负担感到乐观，美国房屋建筑商的信心在 11 月份升至七个月高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/us-homebuilder-sentiment-reaches-seven-month-high-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
