      <title>财政风险迫在眉睫，摩根士丹利下调巴西股票评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/morgan-stanley-downgrades-brazil-stocks-as-fiscal-risks-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利将巴西股票评级下调至减持，并警告称，该国不断扩大的财政赤字可能会压倒央行控制通胀的努力，从而迫使利率上调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/morgan-stanley-downgrades-brazil-stocks-as-fiscal-risks-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 14:47:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
